one_reviews_text: Most value I have ever gotten for a VR game.  If you like tetris and the premise (shooting blocks to change their shape, rather than turning them) then you will enjoy this game.

If you like Tetris, you will like this. I started to take a single look of the game and I found myself trying another level and saying to me that this was the last one just to begin the following. You don't feel time pass and this is good for a game. Fun and simple.
makes a  lot of fun top !
